OL,3,CBritish pro-democracy campaigner Jimmy
OL,4,CLai sentenced to 20 years in Hong Kong
OL,6,FJimmy Lai has been sentenced to 20
OL,7,Fyears in prison.
OL,9,FThe former Hong Kong media boss and
OL,10,FBritish citizen showed no emotion when
OL,11,Fhis sentence was read out. He had
OL,12,Fentered court smiling and waving
OL,13,Ftowards the public gallery, mouthing
OL,14,Fhis thanks and appreciation to those
OL,15,Fwho had come to support him.
