OL,3,CBritish pro-democracy campaigner Jimmy
OL,4,CLai sentenced to 20 years in Hong Kong
OL,6,FAmong those in the public gallery was
OL,7,Fhis wife, Theresa, who appeared upset
OL,8,Fafter his sentence was announced and
OL,9,Fplaced her sunglasses over her eyes.
OL,10,FOthers were openly in tears, still
OL,11,Ftrying to gesture to Jimmy Lai as he
OL,12,Fwas led away.
OL,14,FThe 78-year-old has already spent five
OL,15,Fyears in prison, serving a sentence
OL,16,Ffor fraud. After a trial spanning two
OL,17,Fyears, he was convicted in December on
OL,18,Ftwo counts of colluding with foreign
OL,19,Fforces and one count of sedition.
