OL,3,CBritish pro-democracy campaigner Jimmy
OL,4,CLai sentenced to 20 years in Hong Kong
OL,6,FThe judge sentencing him on those
OL,7,Fcharges on Monday said he will serve
OL,8,F18 years consecutively, following the
OL,9,Fprevious sentence of five years and
OL,10,Fnine months he was given for fraud
OL,11,Fcharges. The prime minister had raised
OL,12,Fthe case during his recent meeting
OL,13,Fwith Chinese President Xi Jinping in
OL,14,FBeijing, appealing on behalf of the
OL,15,FLai family and the British government
OL,16,Ffor Mr Lai to be released. Even to be
OL,17,Fconsidered for humanitarian release,
OL,18,Fgiven his deteriorating health.
