OL,3,CBritish pro-democracy campaigner Jimmy
OL,4,CLai sentenced to 20 years in Hong Kong
OL,6,FThose appeals appear to have made no
OL,7,Fdifference. In court, Mr Lai looked
OL,8,Fmuch thinner than he was at the start
OL,9,Fof his legal proceedings back in
OL,10,FDecember 2023, but he still appeared
OL,11,Fanimated as he sat in the dock and
OL,12,Flooked around to see who was in court
OL,13,Fand spoke with some of his fellow
OL,14,Fdefendants.
OL,16,FSome of his former editors and
OL,17,Fcolleagues from Apple Daily had
OL,18,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to collusion
OL,19,Fcharges. They were given lesser
OL,20,Fsentences, most of around six or seven
OL,21,Fyears.
