OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe Chinese Communist Party has
OL,12,Flabelled Jimmy Lai a traitor and the
OL,13,Fringleader of the protests which
OL,14,Frocked Hong Kong in 2019. Having
OL,15,Fintroduced the National Security law
OL,16,Fto crack down on those protests and
OL,17,Fthe pro-democracy demonstrators
OL,18,Finvolved, it was clear that the man
OL,19,Fthey accused of being the so-called
OL,20,F"mastermind" behind an anti-China
OL,21,Fmovement would receive a long sentence.
