OL,3,CBritish pro-democracy campaigner Jimmy
OL,4,CLai sentenced to 20 years in Hong Kong
OL,6,FHis 20-year sentence is the longest
OL,7,Fhanded down since the National
OL,8,FSecurity Law was introduced. For Jimmy
OL,9,FLai it means he will likely die in
OL,10,Fprison. When he spoke to ITV News in
OL,11,F2020, he knew the authorities would
OL,12,Fseek his arrest, but he still believed
OL,13,Fthat with the support of the
OL,14,Finternational community, justice, and
OL,15,Fhis freedom would prevail.
